videos.description: LeBron James has no words to describe defending Giannis Antetokounmpo when he's hitting jumpers, instead he motions as if he's tipping his cap.

videos.description: After hitting a career-high five 3-pointers against the Lakers, Giannis Antetokounmpo describes how proud he is of the strides he's made in his game.
